#gtts
You pass text and language code (like en for English, ta for Tamil).

gTTS sends a request to Googleâ€™s translate text-to-speech API.

Google generates the speech audio on their servers.

The audio comes back, and gTTS lets you save it as MP3 or play it directly.
#flask
A micro web framework for Python.

Purpose: runs your app on a server and handles web requests.
